[{"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6e27/13a6/557_large.png?m=1608969785", "name": "life", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6e27/13a6/557_normal.png?m=1608969785", "title": "生活", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/life", "topics": 2832, "footer": "", "header": "生活中的技术讨论", "title_alternative": "Life", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6e27/13a6/557_mini.png?m=1608969785", "stars": 745, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 557, "parent_node_name": ""}, "member": {"id": 251120, "username": "LxExExl", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/LxExExl", "website": "", "twitter": "", "psn": "", "github": "", "btc": "", "location": "", "tagline": "", "bio": "", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/3f95/618f/251120_mini.png?m=1641781020", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/3f95/618f/251120_normal.png?m=1641781020", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/3f95/618f/251120_large.png?m=1641781020", "created": 1503883524, "last_modified": 1641781020}, "last_reply_by": "NOspy", "last_touched": 1642191602, "title": "我竟然也遇到了发小借钱 有点难过", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/828212", "created": 1642136402, "deleted": 0, "content": "当然是一开始就没借\r\n\r\n\r\n小学初中同学同桌，后面没联系了。前年组了个群，去年群里没人说话了。\r\n\r\n三天前发消息“在吗”。一般这种消息我都忽略不回。\r\n然后刚才想起来这事，想着还是回一下，毕竟一起坐公交车上学 9 年的互相占座交情。\r\n\r\n\r\n刚才先是语音 40 秒，说酒驾出事要罚金，否则就进去，还有 1 小时。\r\n我开玩笑说没钱，是不是盗号了，我帮忙举报一下账号。\r\n\r\n然后又是 40 秒语音，说真的出事了，要不然也不会这么突然，很久不联系云云。\r\n我回了一张“一滴都没有了”的表情包，结束了对话。\r\n\r\n对方说“行吧，我知道了，你好好的”。结束了对话。\r\n\r\n\r\n那么问题来了，看了虎扑上无数借钱不还的网图搞笑图，我知道借钱是不可能借的，这辈子都不可能借的。甚至我没去问要借多少钱。可是为啥心里还是有点犹豫，有点不忍，有点难过呢？", "content_rendered": "当然是一开始就没借<br /><br /><br />小学初中同学同桌，后面没联系了。前年组了个群，去年群里没人说话了。<br /><br />三天前发消息“在吗”。一般这种消息我都忽略不回。<br />然后刚才想起来这事，想着还是回一下，毕竟一起坐公交车上学 9 年的互相占座交情。<br /><br /><br />刚才先是语音 40 秒，说酒驾出事要罚金，否则就进去，还有 1 小时。<br />我开玩笑说没钱，是不是盗号了，我帮忙举报一下账号。<br /><br />然后又是 40 秒语音，说真的出事了，要不然也不会这么突然，很久不联系云云。<br />我回了一张“一滴都没有了”的表情包，结束了对话。<br /><br />对方说“行吧，我知道了，你好好的”。结束了对话。<br /><br /><br />那么问题来了，看了虎扑上无数借钱不还的网图搞笑图，我知道借钱是不可能借的，这辈子都不可能借的。甚至我没去问要借多少钱。可是为啥心里还是有点犹豫，有点不忍，有点难过呢？", "last_modified": 1642146865, "replies": 127, "id": 828212}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_large.png?m=1641688451", "name": "programmer", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_normal.png?m=1641688451", "title": "程序员", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/programmer", "topics": 47098, "footer": "", "header": "While code monkeys are not eating bananas, they're coding.", "title_alternative": "Programmer", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_mini.png?m=1641688451", "stars": 7666, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 300, "parent_node_name": "computer"}, "member": {"id": 36668, "username": "firhome", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/firhome", "website": "", "twitter": "", "psn": "", "github": "", "btc": "", "location": "", "tagline": "", "bio": "", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/68cd/d7cf/36668_mini.png?m=1587541551", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/68cd/d7cf/36668_normal.png?m=1587541551", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/68cd/d7cf/36668_large.png?m=1587541551", "created": 1364366930, "last_modified": 1587541551}, "last_reply_by": "Gaays", "last_touched": 1642213719, "title": "请教后端同学这种写接口的方式对不对？", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/828191", "created": 1642131855, "deleted": 0, "content": "如：请求一本 book 的订单信息\r\n\r\n [以前] \r\n1.请求后端 bookinfo 接口，bookinfo 返回 data:{}, 包含了 book 的基本信息，book 的订单信息和订单状态(出售中，下架 等)\r\n\r\n2.前端直接渲染数据即可。\r\n\r\n [现在] \r\n1.请求后端 bookinfo 接口 返回 book 基本信息\r\n2.根据 bookinfo 接口获取 book 的 id ，再去请求 bookOrderInfo 获取订单信息\r\n3.根据 book id 和 bookOrderInfo 里面订单 id ，再去请求个接口获取订单状态。\r\n\r\n导致我初始化页面要发 3 个请求。\r\n\r\n想问下  [现在]  这是个什么情况。是后端不愿意给我们包吗？喊他加数据感觉很艰难。很多东西得前端做。如果是这样的话，是不是后面前端可以写 node 来包一层？", "content_rendered": "<p>如：请求一本 book 的订单信息</p>\n<p>[以前]\n1.请求后端 bookinfo 接口，bookinfo 返回 data:{}, 包含了 book 的基本信息，book 的订单信息和订单状态(出售中，下架 等)</p>\n<p>2.前端直接渲染数据即可。</p>\n<p>[现在]\n1.请求后端 bookinfo 接口 返回 book 基本信息\n2.根据 bookinfo 接口获取 book 的 id ，再去请求 bookOrderInfo 获取订单信息\n3.根据 book id 和 bookOrderInfo 里面订单 id ，再去请求个接口获取订单状态。</p>\n<p>导致我初始化页面要发 3 个请求。</p>\n<p>想问下  [现在]  这是个什么情况。是后端不愿意给我们包吗？喊他加数据感觉很艰难。很多东西得前端做。如果是这样的话，是不是后面前端可以写 node 来包一层？</p>\n", "last_modified": 1642131889, "replies": 126, "id": 828191}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6353/8fe6/519_large.png?m=1595507885", "name": "ideas", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6353/8fe6/519_normal.png?m=1595507885", "title": "奇思妙想", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/ideas", "topics": 4789, "footer": "", "header": "让你的创意在这里自由流动吧。", "title_alternative": "Ideas", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6353/8fe6/519_mini.png?m=1595507885", "stars": 2516, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 519, "parent_node_name": "v2ex"}, "member": {"id": 330655, "username": "kujio", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/kujio", "website": null, "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": null, "tagline": null, "bio": null, "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/3631/762b/330655_mini.png?m=1639020367", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/3631/762b/330655_normal.png?m=1639020367", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/3631/762b/330655_large.png?m=1639020367", "avatar_xlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/3631/762b/330655_xlarge.png?m=1639020367", "avatar_xxlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/3631/762b/330655_xlarge.png?m=1639020367", "created": 1532200571, "last_modified": 1639020367}, "last_reply_by": "stabc", "last_touched": 1642199120, "title": "为什么运营商和国家不强制推出统一短信电话朋友圈公众号小程序的 APP 呢？", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/828252", "created": 1642144594, "deleted": 0, "content": "为什么国家不出手三大运营商联合推出一个集电话，短信，朋友圈，公众号，小程序的 APP ，用来打破现在 tx 一家独大的局面，而且也能更方便统一整治账号，游戏，身份认证的乱局。\r\ntx 系现在真的是越来越毒瘤了，在国内环境呵护下长成参天大树，现在仗着体量大，为所欲为了已经。", "content_rendered": "<p>为什么国家不出手三大运营商联合推出一个集电话，短信，朋友圈，公众号，小程序的 APP ，用来打破现在 tx 一家独大的局面，而且也能更方便统一整治账号，游戏，身份认证的乱局。\ntx 系现在真的是越来越毒瘤了，在国内环境呵护下长成参天大树，现在仗着体量大，为所欲为了已经。</p>\n", "last_modified": 1642144594, "replies": 99, "id": 828252}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/ec89/5663/102_large.png?m=1589292852", "name": "git", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/ec89/5663/102_normal.png?m=1589292852", "title": "git", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/git", "topics": 826, "footer": "", "header": "Git is a free and open source distributed version control system designed to handle everything from small to very large projects with speed and efficiency.", "title_alternative": "git", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/ec89/5663/102_mini.png?m=1589292852", "stars": 528, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 102, "parent_node_name": "vcs"}, "member": {"id": 470557, "username": "lingdu666", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/lingdu666", "website": null, "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": null, "tagline": null, "bio": null, "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/4f8a7e772a757f433d5da85599acfc32?s=24&d=retro", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/4f8a7e772a757f433d5da85599acfc32?s=48&d=retro", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/4f8a7e772a757f433d5da85599acfc32?s=73&d=retro", "created": 1582164971, "last_modified": 1582164971}, "last_reply_by": "rrfeng", "last_touched": 1642215689, "title": "git 操作命令行比界面有哪些优势呢？", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/828253", "created": 1642144679, "deleted": 0, "content": "个人理解，重复的很多操作，命令行提炼出一个命令包含多个操作  通过 && 连接，但是界面需要很多重复操作，还有其他优势吗？", "content_rendered": "<p>个人理解，重复的很多操作，命令行提炼出一个命令包含多个操作  通过 &amp;&amp; 连接，但是界面需要很多重复操作，还有其他优势吗？</p>\n", "last_modified": 1642214541, "replies": 96, "id": 828253}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_large.png?m=1641688451", "name": "programmer", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_normal.png?m=1641688451", "title": "程序员", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/programmer", "topics": 47098, "footer": "", "header": "While code monkeys are not eating bananas, they're coding.", "title_alternative": "Programmer", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_mini.png?m=1641688451", "stars": 7666, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 300, "parent_node_name": "computer"}, "member": {"id": 273091, "username": "villivateur", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/villivateur", "website": "https://www.vvzero.com/", "twitter": "", "psn": "", "github": "", "btc": "", "location": "", "tagline": "嵌入式物联网全栈系统工程师", "bio": "", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/233d/26cb/273091_mini.png?m=1635395897", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/233d/26cb/273091_normal.png?m=1635395897", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/233d/26cb/273091_large.png?m=1635395897", "created": 1512652845, "last_modified": 1635395897}, "last_reply_by": "WAHSUN", "last_touched": 1642183771, "title": "求推荐靠谱的域名邮箱服务", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/828181", "created": 1642130291, "deleted": 0, "content": "本来一直用的腾讯企业邮箱，但是腾讯越来越恶心，不绑定微信就不让用，不开启免密登录就隔段时间让你改密码，还捆绑企业微信，准备弃用了。\r\n\r\n需求：\r\n1. 境内直连，服务可用率高；\r\n2. 用户 5 人以下，可接受每月 15 元左右的付费；\r\n3. 支持自定义客户端，如果有网页端更好；\r\n4. 没有上述腾讯企业邮箱这些限制。", "content_rendered": "<p>本来一直用的腾讯企业邮箱，但是腾讯越来越恶心，不绑定微信就不让用，不开启免密登录就隔段时间让你改密码，还捆绑企业微信，准备弃用了。</p>\n<p>需求：</p>\n<ol>\n<li>境内直连，服务可用率高；</li>\n<li>用户 5 人以下，可接受每月 15 元左右的付费；</li>\n<li>支持自定义客户端，如果有网页端更好；</li>\n<li>没有上述腾讯企业邮箱这些限制。</li>\n</ol>\n", "last_modified": 1642130291, "replies": 85, "id": 828181}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6e27/13a6/557_large.png?m=1608969785", "name": "life", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6e27/13a6/557_normal.png?m=1608969785", "title": "生活", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/life", "topics": 2832, "footer": "", "header": "生活中的技术讨论", "title_alternative": "Life", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6e27/13a6/557_mini.png?m=1608969785", "stars": 745, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 557, "parent_node_name": ""}, "member": {"id": 535964, "username": "fy1206", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/fy1206", "website": "", "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": "", "tagline": "", "bio": "", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/aecd/00dc/535964_mini.png?m=1637837357", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/aecd/00dc/535964_normal.png?m=1637837357", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/aecd/00dc/535964_large.png?m=1637837357", "created": 1614844346, "last_modified": 1637837357}, "last_reply_by": "fy1206", "last_touched": 1642167582, "title": "心浮气躁的时候，你是怎么静下来的？", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/828183", "created": 1642130364, "deleted": 0, "content": "不管在生活中，还是工作中。大部分事情都是需要静下心来完成的，否则要么三天打鱼两天筛网，要么半途而废，而且效率非常低。相信大家也有过浮躁，有时间可能自己发现了想去解决这个问题，但是时间不长又开始浮躁。每个人对浮躁的定位不同，有的人认为工作累了可以适当放松一下，有的人认为只要松懈了就难以达到以前的状态。\r\n大家平时是怎么静下来的？", "content_rendered": "<p>不管在生活中，还是工作中。大部分事情都是需要静下心来完成的，否则要么三天打鱼两天筛网，要么半途而废，而且效率非常低。相信大家也有过浮躁，有时间可能自己发现了想去解决这个问题，但是时间不长又开始浮躁。每个人对浮躁的定位不同，有的人认为工作累了可以适当放松一下，有的人认为只要松懈了就难以达到以前的状态。\n大家平时是怎么静下来的？</p>\n", "last_modified": 1642147147, "replies": 55, "id": 828183}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/a3c6/5c29/108_large.png?m=1635654723", "name": "bb", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/a3c6/5c29/108_normal.png?m=1635654723", "title": "宽带症候群", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/bb", "topics": 10194, "footer": "", "header": "网速很重要。比快更快。", "title_alternative": "Broadband Symptom Complex", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/a3c6/5c29/108_mini.png?m=1635654723", "stars": 5325, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 108, "parent_node_name": "geek"}, "member": {"id": 254690, "username": "waynevan", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/waynevan", "website": null, "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": null, "tagline": null, "bio": null, "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/761124d76b3ae056038a5cdc2e5b1645?s=24&d=retro", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/761124d76b3ae056038a5cdc2e5b1645?s=48&d=retro", "avatar_large": "https: